targets.rawSql:
with tabela as (
  select count(*) as total,
  (select count(*) from lambda_inv a
   where existe and  exists (select 1 from lambda_inv b where a.role_nova = b.role_nova and a.name <> b.name)) as ajustar
   from lambda_inv where existe
)
select ajustar as Ajustar, total-ajustar as OK from tabela
